Summary: came in high in sky from sw turned east and went east
divs: Sighting Detailsstanding on porch and my wife saw it. It was brighter than the stars and moving in our direction from the southwest. in about a min or so it turned east and went across the sky. must have watched it for 5 min before the sky line had covered its course,
